// 4 riksmal (jenten, boken, gaten, solen), 2 bokmal (gata, sola) -> flag both bokmal
{"id":"nb-drift-pos-020","text":"Jenten var glad. Boken var pen. Gaten var lang. Solen skinte. Gata var tom. Sola var fin.","expected":[{"rule_id":"doc-drift-nb-register","start":62,"end":66,"suggestion":"gaten"},{"rule_id":"doc-drift-nb-register","start":76,"end":80,"suggestion":"solen"}],"status":"ok"}

// ── Positive: lexical markers contribute to majority but are deduped ──

// 4 markers total: 3 bokmal morphological (jenta, boka, gata) + 1 riksmal lexical (efter, caught by typo)
// + 1 riksmal morphological (solen) -> after solen only survives doc-drift
// Actually: jenta=bokmal, boka=bokmal, gata=bokmal, efter=riksmal(typo dedupes), solen=riksmal
// Majority = bokmal(3), minority = riksmal(2), solen is the only doc-drift survivor
{"id":"nb-drift-pos-021","text":"Jenta gikk hjem. Boka var god. Gata var tom. Solen skinte.","expected":[{"rule_id":"doc-drift-nb-register","start":45,"end":50,"suggestion":"sola"}],"status":"ok"}

// riksmal lexical markers (efter, sne) + riksmal morphological (boken, gaten) = 4 riksmal
// bokmal morphological (jenta) = 1 bokmal -> flag jenta
{"id":"nb-drift-pos-022","text":"Boken var god. Gaten var lang. Jenta gikk hjem.","expected":[{"rule_id":"doc-drift-nb-register","start":31,"end":36,"suggestion":"jenten"}],"status":"ok"}

// Mixed: 3 bokmal (jenta, boka, gata), riksmal "sne" (typo deduped) but count still helps
// If only 3 bokmal and no riksmal morphological -> no drift (all markers same register)
// Need to add riksmal morphological marker too
{"id":"nb-drift-pos-023","text":"Jenta gikk hjem. Boka var god. Gata var tom. Boken var fin.","expected":[{"rule_id":"doc-drift-nb-register","start":45,"end":50,"suggestion":"boka"}],"status":"ok"}

